headline.main: Lawmakers Call on U.S. Marines to Investigate Nude Photo Network
headline.print_headline: Lawmakers Call on U.S. Marines to Investigate Nude Photo Network

lead_paragraph: Senior U.S. lawmakers on Sunday condemned the suspected distribution of nude photographs of female Marines to military personnel and veterans via a social media network that promotes sexual violence, and called on the Marine Corps to fully investigate.
